profile.bio: Noel Rappin is the Director of Talent at Table XI. Noel is the author of Rails 4 Test Prescriptions, Master Space and Time With JavaScript", and Trust-Driven Development. Follow Noel on Twitter @noelrap, and online at http://www.noelrappin.com.
